===I want to buy...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Misha:''' I want to buy a big storage chest
:{Choice} You've got too many things?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' You've got too many things?
:'''Misha:''' Yeah! With the exploding cloud candies that the customer gave me yesterday, my drawers are already stuffed full of souvenirs from various planets...
:'''Misha:''' I split some into smaller portions. I'll bring you some when I see you next time!
:'''Misha:''' They taste a bit like a spicier version of mint, but the aftertaste is surprisingly fresh and sweet! This flavor matches the impression I get from that customer perfectly
:'''Misha:''' He was tall and strong with a ferocious expression and a great ax on his back. He looked a lot like Boss Stone
:'''Misha:''' I spent a lot of time preparing myself mentally before going to help him...
:{Choice} Interesting contrast
:'''(Trailblazer):''' A customer like that gifting you sweets. It's got a nice contrast to it
:'''Misha:''' It does. I was super cautious when I asked if he wanted help taking his luggage up! When I realized he was the silent type, I got even more scared and actually tripped over. When I climbed back to my feet, I realized that the customer had already taken his luggage and taken the lift upstairs...
:'''Misha:''' Thankfully I didn't make any mistakes when I went to clean his room and I even fixed his Dreamscape room clock. When I went back, he was not there, but he had left a pack of exploding cloud candy for me. I breathed huge a sigh of relief... That kind of recognition felt amazing!
:'''Misha:''' Do you think... if I keep working hard like this, I'll receive enough candies from guests to cover me for the rest of my life?
:{Choice} Yes, but your teeth will rot
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Probably, but your teeth will rot! Kids should take better care of their teeth!
::'''Misha:''' I'm not a kid anymore! I may have had tooth decay before, but I've been careful ever since!
::'''Misha:''' Ah, I have to go and greet guests. Talk to you again soon!
:{Choice} Yeah! You're amazing!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Yeah! Because you're amazing!
::'''Misha:''' Hehe, hearing you say that makes me feel so proud! It's more that the guests put up with me, though
::'''Misha:''' Thank you for your approval though. I need to go and greet guests. Talk to you again soon!
:'''Misha:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 03.png|80px]]
}}
