===Are you there...? Excuse...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Misha:''' Are you there...? Excuse me, I wanted to ask if there are any recommendations for things I'll need for traveling?
:{Choice} The Express has everything
::'''(Trailblazer):''' The Express has everything you need. You don't need to bring anything
::'''Misha:''' They even prepare a change of clothes? The Express really is the best!
::'''Misha:''' Although, hearing you say that makes me worry even more... Ah, what else do I need to take with me?
:{Choice} Phone, credits, a baseball bat...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Phone, credits, a baseball bat! They're all pretty practical, right?
::'''Misha:''' Yeah! Communications, currency, and an item for self-defense... are all absolute necessities!
::'''Misha:''' But these things aside, what else will I need...
:'''Misha:''' I finally got a short amount of vacation time, but I haven't even decided where I want to travel to!
:'''Misha:''' I want to prepare my luggage, then select my destination. Then, I can just set off right away!
:{Choice} Would you like to come with us?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Would you like to come with us? We'll leave tomorrow!
::'''Misha:''' That's very tempting, but I only have three days... I don't think that's very suitable for long-distance travel
:{Choice} You could vacation in the hotel
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You could actually spend your holiday in the hotel
::'''Misha:''' That's a really good idea... I may have worked here for a long time, but I've never enjoyed the hotel's services as a guest before!
::'''Misha:''' I just know there are lots of exciting things to explore. Just thinking about it makes me so happy!!!
:{Choice} Are you not scared traveling alone?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Are you not scared traveling alone? What if you run into bad people?
::'''Misha:''' I'm not scared! I decided I am going to learn from you, (Trailblazer)! I'm going to buy a baseball bat to protect myself!
:{Choice} Remember to send pictures
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Remember to send me pictures
:'''(Trailblazer):''' No matter where you are, pictures can always bring us closer together
:'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Message Misha 40.png|256px]]
:'''Misha:''' ...A solitary and frozen land... do these Snow Plains have a name? What planet are they on? Can you visit without an invitation?
:{Choice} You can go whenever you like
:'''(Trailblazer):''' These Snow Plains are on the planet Jarilo-VI, outside the town of Belobog. You are free to go whenever you like
:'''Misha:''' Great. I have to go and see this place!
:'''Misha:''' Speaking with you makes me so happy! It feels like I've already started on my dream adventure. You have to tell me more next time!
}}
